snippet.title: Close your eyes or you die - The Secret Door - Official GAMEPLAY Trailer
snippet.description:
From the indie horror game "The Secret Door" developed in Unreal Engine 5. 

Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2254300/The_Secret_Door/

Twitter:
https://twitter.com/FlamProductions

The Secret Door is a Realistic Horror Game made in Unreal Engine 5. You need to close your eyes when you see demons, otherwise you are in danger. Demo available now on Steam.
Are you ready to open the door?

#unrealengine5 #horrorgaming #indiegame
